---
/**
 * AboutHero — page H1 + tagline. Top of the About editorial column.
 *
 * The tagline uses `var(--font-serif)` per PHASE-1-ROADMAP §2.R2; the page
 * sets `includeSerif=true` on PageShell so Instrument Serif is preloaded.
 */
---

<header class="about-hero">
  <h1>About GyanDev</h1>
  <p class="about-hero__tagline">
    Deep notes for modern developers — built by developers, for developers.
  </p>
</header>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .about-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .about-hero__tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.375rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
